":"gold","text":"If POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL hear its echoing cry, they respond by gather\u00ad ing from far and wide."},{"version":"silver","text":"Whenever three or more of these get together, they sing in a loud voice that sounds like bellowing."},{"version":"crystal","text":"When it expands its throat to croak out a tune, nearby POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL gather immediately."},{"version":"ruby","text":"The curled hair on POLITOED\u2019s head is proof of its status as a king. It is said that the longer and more curled the hair, the more respect this POK\u00e9MON earns from its peers."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"The curled hair on POLITOED\u2019s head is proof of its status as a king. It is said that the longer and more curled the hair, the more respect this POK\u00e9MON earns from its peers."},{"version":"emerald","text":"The curled hair on its head proves its status as a king. It is said that the longer and curlier the hair, the more respect it earns from its peers."},{"version":"firered","text":"Whenever three or more of these get together, they sing in a loud voice that sounds like bellowing."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"If POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL hear its echoing cry, they respond by gathering from far and wide."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It gathers groups of others as their leader. Its cries make POLIWAG obey."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It gathers groups of others as their leader. Its cries make POLIWAG obey."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It gathers groups of others as their leader. Its cries make POLIWAG obey."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"If POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL hear its echoing cry, they respond by gathering from far and wide."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Whenever three or more of these get together, they sing in a loud voice that sounds like bellowing."},{"version":"black","text":"It gathers groups of others as their leader. Its cries make Poliwag obey."},{"version":"white","text":"It gathers groups of others as their leader. Its cries make Poliwag obey."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It gathers groups of others as their leader. Its cries make Poliwag obey."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It gathers groups of others as their leader. Its cries make Poliwag obey."},{"version":"x","text":"Whenever three or more of these get together, they sing in a loud voice that sounds like bellowing."},{"version":"y","text":"If Poliwag and Poliwhirl hear its echoing cry, they respond by gathering from far and wide."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"The curled hair on Politoed\u2019s head is proof of its status as a king. It is said that the longer and more curled the hair, the more respect this Pok\u00e9mon earns from its peers."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"The curled hair on Politoed\u2019s head is proof of its status as a king. It is said that the longer and more curled the hair, the more respect this Pok\u00e9mon earns from its peers."},{"version":"sun","text":"They gather on moonlit nights to form a large chorus. Their cries sound angry and not at all pleasant, but they are certainly distinctive."},{"version":"moon","text":"It\u2019s the leader of Poliwag and Poliwhirl. When Politoed roars, they all cower in fear."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Although its cries sound like screams, a composer created a beautiful ballad that was influenced by the sounds."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"The longer and more luxurious the curled hair on its head, the greater the number of Poliwag and Poliwhirl that will obey it."},{"version":"sword","text":"At nightfall, these Pok\u00e9mon appear on the shores of lakes. They announce their territorial claims by letting out cries that sound like shouting."},{"version":"shield","text":"The cry of a male is louder than that of a female. Male Politoed with deep, menacing voices find more popularity with the opposite gender."}],"evo":{"name":"poliwag","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":nul